Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5/4 14:32 [櫻見遊樂園]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天… 為什麼是藍的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 降落傘打不開咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 一會兒我們別坐那麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你有聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇林會化掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來坐那個吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 為什麼會在這裡呢
